cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PDSCH antenna ports XP to a negative value will cause configuration validation errors and prevent the DU from initializing properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PDSCH 天線端口 XP 設定為負值會導致配置驗證錯誤，並阻止 DU 正確初始化。
